[I] Intel Graphics System Firmware Update Library

[T] Intel Graphics System Firmware Update Library (IGSC FUL) is a pure C low
[T] level library that exposes a required API to perform a firmware update of
[T] an Intel discrete graphics device. It uses a cross platform library metee
[T] in order to access the GSC (mei) device. GSC device is an extension of the
[T] Intel discrete graphics device (dGFX).

[U] https://github.com/intel/igsc

[A] intel
